reviewText: Dil was a new character from the Rugrats series that has 5 episodes that centered on him!
I love the episodes I have this one on VHS
I ordered this VHS around December- Early in January... got a chance to watch it yesterday and it was pretty funny! Love all the Rugrats!
My grandson loved the movie. It was in excellent condition, sleeve and tape both. A hit for any 5 year old who loves the Rugrats.
